    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738580",
        "quote": "Eliza Factor's first novel, 'The Mercury Fountain,' explores what happens when a life driven by ideology confronts implacable truths of science and human nature. It also shows how leaders can inflict damage by neglecting the real needs of real people.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Floyd Skloot",
            "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738580"
