    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738581",
        "quote": "Fiction about mining has a long tradition - Emile Zola's 'Germinal' and Upton Sinclair's 'King Coal' come to mind - and most readers will be aware of the industry's harsh conditions.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Floyd Skloot",
            "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738581"
