    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738582",
        "quote": "Science trumps magical thinking: there was a reason the Incas called their mercury mine 'la mina de los muertos,' the mine of the dead. Building a life and a community upon principles that ignore such realities is doomed to fail.",
