    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738571",
        "quote": "I've forgotten what it's like to remember. I've lost the mindless confidence that a moment, an idea, a thought will be there for me later, the bravado of breezing through experience in the certainty that it will become part of my self, part of my story.",
