    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738564",
        "quote": "In 1964, at the age of 39, Flannery O'Connor died from complications of lupus. She had lived with this autoimmune disease for 14 years, primarily confined to her mother's farm, Andalusia, in Milledgeville, Ga.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Floyd Skloot",
            "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738564"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Had",
                "url": "/topics/had"
