                "name": "Had",
                "url": "/topics/had"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738554",
        "quote": "My cerebral cortex, the gray matter that MIT neuroscientist Steven Pinker likens to 'a large sheet of two-dimensional tissue that has been wadded up to fit inside the spherical skull,' is riddled instead of whole.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Floyd Skloot",
            "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738554"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
