                "url": "/topics/tissue"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738555",
        "quote": "I became demented overnight. Sudden onset is one factor that distinguishes my form of dementia from the more common form associated with Alzheimer's disease.",
