    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738559",
        "quote": "Through his long, productive career, Paul Theroux has mixed nonfiction books about exotic travel with novels set in exotic places. Africa, Singapore, Hong Kong, Honduras - he lives in and writes about places most of us never see.",
