    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738567",
        "quote": "When Beverly and I got together in 1992, and I moved to be with her in the little round house she'd built in the middle of 20 acres of woods near Amity, I found myself immersed in a natural setting that I responded to with all my being.",
