    {
        "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738570",
        "quote": "I think one of the primary themes in my work is the paradox of memory, at once fundamental to our sense of who we are and yet elusive, ever-changing, fragmentary. One way to look at this is to say that, therefore, we ourselves are elusive, ever-changing and fragmentary to ourselves.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Floyd Skloot",
            "url": "/quotes/floyd_skloot_738570"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
